Package snid

Class Citizen

  • java.lang.Object
    • snid.Person
      • snid.Citizen
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Citizen>
    public class Citizen
extends Person
implements java.lang.Comparable<Citizen>
    The class representing a citizen of the country. A citizen is also a Person. Their data can be compared to another person in the system.
